# Layout composition

When composing page layouts with **Harmony Astro components**:

- **Spacing:** Use Harmony tokens only — `var(--space-N)`. No arbitrary `px`, `rem`, or `em` values.
- **Cards:** No Card nested inside Card.
- **Content area order:** Page header is always the first child in the content area. Button bar is always the last child.
- **Multi-card layouts:** Use design system grid patterns with token-based gaps.
- **Imports:** Verify all imported components are used.
- **Components:** Import from `src/components/ui/` and layouts from `src/layouts/`.
